data.description: *** Fresh Interior Paint *** Plus a 3.625% Assumable Mortgage is Available! ***  Nestled in the charming community of Dayton, this 3-bed 2-bath home offers a generous 1,656 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space.  Constructed in 2019, it showcases the latest architectural trends and quality craftsmanship: drought-resistant front landscaping, a level backyard with a patio, lush grass, and a drip-irrigated retaining wall.  Close to schools, a dog park, a community haven, and shops. Approaching the property, you'll be greeted by the striking drought-resistant landscaping in the front yard. Not only does this feature enhance the curb appeal, but it also speaks to the property's commitment to sustainability. The vibrant assortment of flora complements the contemporary façade, creating an inviting entrance.  Step inside, where a world of comfort and style unfolds. The spacious open floor plan effortlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, promoting interaction and versatility. Natural light streams through large windows, highlighting the tasteful interior finishes. The living room exudes warmth, making it an ideal space for relaxation and entertaining. Whether you're hosting a movie night or a gathering with friends, this area caters to every occasion.  The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen, complete with modern stainless steel appliances, ample cabinetry, and a large amount of counter space. It's a culinary haven where you can experiment with flavors and create memorable dishes. The adjacent dining area is perfect for intimate family meals or larger gatherings.  A glass door provides seamless access to the outdoor haven.  Speaking of the outdoors, the backyard is a true oasis. The level expanse features a beautifully paved patio, providing the perfect setting for al fresco dining, morning coffees, or evening conversations under the stars. Beyond the patio, a lush carpet of grass invites outdoor activities and relaxation. The crowning jewel is the retaining wall, thoughtfully plumbed with a drip irrigation system, ensuring your garden flourishes effortlessly. This space beckons gardening enthusiasts to bring their creative visions to life.  A tranquil haven awaits in the bedroom wing of the home. The primary suite is a sanctuary of comfort, boasting a generous layout and an en-suite bathroom. With a soothing color palette and ample natural light, this space offers a respite from the demands of daily life. The en-suite bathroom exudes spa-like luxury, featuring modern fixtures, a walk-in shower, a separate tub, and tasteful finishes.  Two additional bedrooms offer versatility, accommodating family members and guests or serving as a home office or fitness area. The second bathroom, thoughtfully designed, caters to the needs of the household and guests alike.  One of the many advantages of this residence is its prime location. Situated a short distance from the local elementary, middle, and high schools, it provides the convenience every family desires. A dog park is within easy reach, making it simple to keep your furry companions active and engaged. The nearby community park offers many recreational options, from playgrounds to picnic areas, creating an inviting space for socializing and relaxation.  For those who enjoy retail therapy or need to run errands, a variety of retailers are conveniently situated nearby. From boutiques to grocery stores, everything you need is within easy reach. This central location ensures you can easily access amenities without compromising the tranquility of your neighborhood.  In conclusion, this exceptional 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers an unparalleled combination of modern living, thoughtful design, and unbeatable convenience. With its stylish interior, captivating outdoor spaces, and proximity to schools, parks, and shops, it presents a unique opportunity to embrace a lifestyle of comfort and ease. Your dream home journey starts here!
